{{#> layout}}
    <h2>Security Alert</h2>
    
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    
    <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <p><strong>Important Security Notice:</strong> We detected a {{alertType}} on your account.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info">
        <table class="table">
            <tr>
                <th>Event Type:</th>
                <td>{{alertType}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Date & Time:</th>
                <td>{{formatDate date}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Location:</th>
                <td>{{location}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Device:</th>
                <td>{{device}}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info">
        <p><strong>Details:</strong><br>{{details}}</p>
    </div>

    {{#if requiresAction}}
    <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <p><strong>Action Required:</strong> Please take immediate action to secure your account.</p>
    </div>

    <p>For your security, please:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Log in to your account and review recent activity</li>
        <li>Change your password immediately</li>
        <li>Enable two-factor authentication if not already enabled</li>
        <li>Review and update your security settings</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="{{securitySettingsUrl}}" class="button">Review Security Settings</a>
    {{/if}}

    <p><strong>Recommended Security Measures:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Use a strong, unique password</li>
        <li>Enable biometric authentication in the mobile app</li>
        <li>Keep your contact information up to date</li>
        <li>Monitor your account regularly</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <p><strong>If you don't recognize this activity:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Contact our security team immediately at {{securityContactNumber}}</li>
            <li>Change your password immediately</li>
            <li>Review all recent transactions</li>
            <li>Check for any unauthorized changes to your account settings</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <p>To report suspicious activity or speak with our security team:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Call: {{securityContactNumber}} (24/7 Security Hotline)</li>
        <li>Email: {{securityEmail}}</li>
        <li>Visit: Your nearest branch</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Your security is our top priority.</strong> We continuously monitor your account for suspicious activity and will alert you to any concerns.</p>

    <div class="alert alert-info">
        <p><strong>Security Tip:</strong> We will never ask for your password, PIN, or full account details via email or phone.</p>
    </div>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The Mobile Banking Security Team</p>
{{/layout}}
